# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files. Without this, Windows'
# core.autocrlf checks files out as CRLF, which breaks LF-only tooling (biome's
# `bun run check`) and churns diffs. git auto-detects binary files and leaves them alone.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never apply text/EOL filters.
*.webp binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
